Question: One image features one golf ball in the middle surrounded by at least five other balls in a circle-type formation.

Reference Answer: True

Right image URL: http://image.ec21.com/image/kaisun/oimg_GC06247211_CA06247235/Mini_Golf_Balls.jpg

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many golf balls are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many golf balls are in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 1 and {ANSWER1} == 1')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are there at least five other balls surrounding the golf ball in a circle-type formation?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are there at least five other balls surrounding the golf ball in a circle-type formation?')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER2} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER2} and {ANSWER4}')
ANSWER7=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER5} xor {ANSWER6}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER7)
```
